{"tid":2302297,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"ACO 師？！ Out 啦！ 我黎推工人師","createTime":"2020-11-27T04:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T09:31:48.000Z","uid":205272,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce98e908fd5d09d6c6ce59af0e1ec24520d271c0","tid":2302297,"uid":205272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"我又黎推工人師。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工人除左狗署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、油政（部門西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）、LCSD（成日搬鐵馬）、運吉（部門西）、水記渠務（污水、厭惡性質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）、食環（執屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）、衛生（上前線送死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）、稅局（部門西）、漁農（鐘意喂蚊除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）、教育局（學校成日搬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）、邪教（陪人坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），其他部門都可以申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工人師有咩好處：<br />\n1）公屋/綠表最快：ACO 師生埋仔點都要5年（公屋）、10年年資（綠表居屋）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工人師只需3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無聽錯，結婚唔生都係3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公屋/綠表任君選擇<br />\n2）地位最高：大家有無玩過鬥獸棋，工人就好似老鼠咁惡，署長都買你怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，過左試用期橫行無忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3）光明正大秘撈：工人師其中一項職責係茶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你如果負責搞茶水就發啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽聞茶水既收入都可以有時有幾千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1）每周45 工作時數，朝八晚六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2）頂薪八年萬六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：速大20 商科FG，中佬。六年多個政府部門工作經驗，9 沖工人但未試過有interview <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係唔係要出去做吓順豐、OA 先有得去interview<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0525558755f7fb114f7ab067ff80614166c4e8ee","tid":2302297,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"On9 CS工人位9成請NCSC工人"},{"pid":"758920f7f8f1c9fa77a20077fc70f1185c981285","tid":2302297,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:36:54.000Z","msg":"有公屋等於每月收入多一萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926ec320d103f1c989ca65852718ee5d346dea42","tid":2302297,"uid":205272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0525558755f7fb114f7ab067ff80614166c4e8ee","tid":2302297,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"On9 CS工人位9成請NCSC工人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"識人做屋邨花王考到工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1bcf742b538a8766b48760e40f18488af62befa","tid":2302297,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"926ec320d103f1c989ca65852718ee5d346dea42","tid":2302297,"uid":205272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0525558755f7fb114f7ab067ff80614166c4e8ee","tid":2302297,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T04:24:59.000Z","msg